title: Fruhstuck und Mittags Bei Mir
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, Indian, Organic, Take-out
description: A vegetarian/vegan restaurant offers small breakfast/lunch choices which are mostly vegan. Uses only organic or natural products. Soy milk for coffees available. Has a daily changing lunch special (only sometimes vegan, check website) and always has vegan masala dosa (Indian pancake).
